---
title: Butternut Squash Stuffed Pasta with Toasted Pine Nuts and Baby Heirloom Tomatoes
description: We love tomatoes all year long here at HelloFresh. This dish combines some of our favourite pairings. Creamy Parmesan, sweet baby heirloom tomatoes and basil pesto make it feel like summer. A little squeeze of lemon at the end brings the whole dish together!
